{"arkId":"cl020018318","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl020018318","modified ":"2025-08-19","title":"Portrait du roi de Rome (1811-1832) de face","titleComplement":null,"denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Portrait du roi de Rome (1811-1832) de face"}],"displayDateCreated":"1811","currentLocation":"Petit format","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1811,"endYear":"","text":null,"type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Prud\u0027hon, Pierre-Paul","attributionLevel":"attribution actuelle","linkType":"original","dates":[{"date":"1823","place":"Paris","type":"date 2"},{"date":"1758","place":"Cluny","type":"date 1"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q469056"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 4650, Recto","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"Inv. fran\u00e7ais, t. XIII 2083","type":"Num\u00e9ros de catalogues"},{"value":"vol.20, p.260","type":"R\u00e9f\u00e9rence de l\u0027inventaire manuscrit"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Arts graphiques","printsDrawingsEntity":"Cabinet des dessins","printsDrawingsCollection":"Fonds des dessins et miniatures","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"0.108","displayDimension":"0.108 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0.108","displayDimension":"0.108 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"\u00e0 la feuille","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":"","note":""}],"shape":"circulaire","materialsAndTechniques":"Crayons noir et blanc, estompe, sur papier bleu d\u00e9color\u00e9. Forme ronde. Inscription au revers (relev\u00e9e dans l\u0027inventaire, elle n\u0027est plus conserv\u00e9e avec le dessin) : \u0027Le roi de Rome n\u00e9 le 20 Mars 1811 dessin\u00e9 d\u0027apr\u00e8s nature \u00e0 l\u0027\u00e2ge de 4 mois par P. Prud\u0027hon, peintre de l\u0027imp\u00e9ratrice Jos\u00e9phine (sic). Ce dessin a servi d\u0027\u00e9tude pour le tableau peint en 1811 par Prud\u0027hon et grav\u00e9 en 1825 par Achille Lef\u00e8vre qui repr\u00e9sente le petit roi couch\u00e9 sur un manteau de velours brod\u00e9 dans un jardin et environn\u00e9 de fleurs imp\u00e9riales. Vente de Boisfremont, l\u00e9gataire de Prud\u0027hon, 1864 - Cf. Edmond de Goncourt ; Cat. de l\u0027oeuvre de Prud\u0027hon, p. 71. V. ibid. p. 41 sur la peinture.\u0027","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Ch.-P. Le Boulanger de Boisfremont (L. 353) ; vente de sa fille, Mme Power, Paris, 15-16 avril 1864, n\u00b0 6, adjug\u00e9 126 F non \u00e0 Mme Denain (Guiffrey), mais \u00e0 Henry Didier, qui en 1867, le pr\u00eate \u00e0 l\u0027exposition de Malmaison (n\u00b0 75, \u0027provenant de la vente de Boisfremont\u0027). Appartient en tous cas \u00e0 Mme Derain en 1874 (exp.) ; sa vente apr\u00e8s d\u00e9c\u00e8s, Paris, galerie Georges Petit, 6-7 avril 1893, n\u00b0 38, adjug\u00e9 1800 F \u00e0 Mme Hippolyte Adam ; Dr. Antonin Clerc (1871-1954) et sa famille ; don en m\u00e9moire de (leurs parents) M. et Mme Hippolyte Adam de Boulogne-sur-Mer en avril 1919 (L. 1886 a).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Clerc, Antonin","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1919,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"collection":[{"value":"Boulanger"},{"value":"Denain, Madame"},{"value":"Adam, Hippolyte, Mme"},{"value":"Boisfremont, Charles Boulanger de"},{"value":"Power, Emilie"},{"value":"Denain"},{"value":"Didier, Henry"}],"place":[{"value":"New York, Metropolitan Museum of Art, oeuvre en rapport"},{"value":"Paris+"},{"value":"Rome+"},{"value":"Malmaison, Mus\u